  <subsection>
            <title>Repetition</title>
            <p>Repetition is when a process repeats itself until a desired outcome is reached. In programming, repetition is achieved through loops. A <term>loop</term> allows an algorithm to repeat certain actions until a specified condition is met. Another term commonly used for repetition is <term>iteration</term>.</p>

